Review: Great road trip movie! Some of the monologues are so great!
Jacco de Paris is the coolest guy ever! Wish I was more like him tbh

I read the script then watched this, so that made me like this a little less. Felt more like a play than a movie (I guess it kinda is supposed to be like that) but didn’t do anything super interesting with the film medium imo.
Wish I saw this in the theater, action kinda mid on the computer
Kinda thought this would be boring tbh, but was absolutely enthralled and bought into the world immensely.
